snippet: Leo Komarov broke a tie as the host Toronto Maple Leafs beat the Rangers, 5-4, on Saturday in a game in which both teams struggled with the lead.
abstract: NHL Roundup; Toronto Maple Leafs beat New York Rangers, 5-4; other hockey scores noted.
